        {
            "review_id": "227394382",
            "steam_id": "76561198059689082",
            "playtime_minutes": 3231,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 1,
            "weighted_score": 0.523809552192688,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "A turning point for the series, it’s just as you remember it, a timeless classic and probably the best way to play it today.\n\nThat said, the game doesn’t pull any punches, some levels are genuinely tough and will require you to restart several times and adapt your strategy on the fly, but everything else: the factions, the maps, the combat system, the magic is still there.\n\nOn the downside, the absence of extra campaigns that were included in the previous Complete Edition and which continue the story, which detracts from what is otherwise a great release\n\n"
        },
        {
            "review_id": "227108433",
            "steam_id": "76561199665839745",
            "playtime_minutes": 215795,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "HIGHLY RECOMMEND, This game was one of my favourites growing up and remains a favourite today. Nostalgia combined with being able to customize a game to your time availability has me sold."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "226745848",
